      <title>独家：消息人士称，计费软件公司 Zuora 正在考虑收购后出售</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/billing-software-firm-zuora-explores-sale-after-takeover-interest-sources-say-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，为企业提供订阅管理软件的 Zuora 正在探索包括在收到潜在收购者的收购意向后出售在内的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/billing-software-firm-zuora-explores-sale-after-takeover-interest-sources-say-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
