      <title>英国皇家邮政所有者拒绝捷克亿万富翁克雷廷斯基的收购要约</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/daniel-kretinsky-explores-bid-royal-mail-owner-sources-say-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位了解该计划的消息人士周三表示，捷克亿万富翁丹尼尔·克雷廷斯基(Daniel Kretinsky)正在努力改善对英国皇家邮政(Royal Mail)所有者的收购要约，此前他的投资工具表示本月已提出不具约束力的收购要约，但遭到拒绝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/daniel-kretinsky-explores-bid-royal-mail-owner-sources-say-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 10:07:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国地区银行预计商业地产损失和贷款销售增加</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-regional-banks-seen-booking-more-commercial-property-losses-loan-sales-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于硅谷银行和 Signature Bank 倒闭一年后该行业仍面临压力，美国地区银行预计将拨出更多资金来弥补潜在的商业房地产 (CRE) 损失，并出售更多房地产贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-regional-banks-seen-booking-more-commercial-property-losses-loan-sales-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 10:02:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国汽车制造商一汽汽车金融部门推出无首付贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-faws-auto-finance-unit-launches-loan-with-no-down-payment-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国有汽车制造商一汽集团的汽车金融部门推出了无首付贷款计划，成为自政府取消最低还款额以来首批采取此举措的供应商之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-faws-auto-finance-unit-launches-loan-with-no-down-payment-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:04:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>第一生命保险首席执行官预计主动收购将成为日本的普遍做法</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/dai-ichi-life-ceo-expects-unsolicited-takeovers-become-common-practice-japan-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第一生命保险首席执行官在以出乎意料的出价成功达成 20 亿美元收购一家公司的交易后表示，随着时间的推移，由于政府努力消除这种做法的污名，主动收购将在日本变得普遍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/dai-ichi-life-ceo-expects-unsolicited-takeovers-become-common-practice-japan-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:05:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>G20监管机构称“非银行机构”应持有更多现金以应对利润率飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/g20-watchdog-says-non-banks-should-hold-more-cash-cope-with-margin-spikes-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[二十国集团金融监管机构周三提议，保险公司、对冲基金、家族办公室和大宗商品交易商等“非银行”应持有足够的现金，并制定应急计划，以应对用于支持衍生品头寸的抵押品激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/g20-watchdog-says-non-banks-should-hold-more-cash-cope-with-margin-spikes-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:02:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
